The spelling of   Elizabeth   used in the Authorized Version of the New Testament, and in most modern European languages. This was the name of the mother of John the Baptist (Luke 1:60). Etymologically, the name means ‘God is my oath’, and is therefore identical with <i>Elisheba</i>, the name of the wife of Aaron according to the genealogy at Exodus 6:23. The final element seems to have been altered by association with Hebrew <i>shabbāth</i> ‘Sabbath’."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Elizabeth Denebawdo was born in 1354, in Devon, England, United Kingdom as the daughter of Denebawdo. She had at least 1 son with John Keynes. She died before July 1416."},"et":{"1354–Bef. Jul 1416":"1354–enne juulit 1416","1354–1416":"1354–1416","1380–1420":"1380–1420","1405–1425":"1405–1425","–Male":"Surnud","1425":"1425","1354":"1354","1420":"1420","1380":"1380","Bef. Jul 1416":"enne juulit 1416","1405":"1405","1416":"1416","Winkley, Devons, England":"Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Winkleigh, Devon, England":"Winkleigh, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1354–Bef. Jul 1416":"1354–ennen vuotta heinäkuu 1416","1354–1416":"1354–1416","1380–1420":"1380–1420","1405–1425":"1405–1425","–Male":"Kuollut","1425":"1425","1354":"1354","1420":"1420","1380":"1380","Bef. Jul 1416":"ennen vuotta heinäkuu 1416","1405":"1405","1416":"1416","Winkley, Devons, England":"Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Winkleigh, Devon, England":"Winkleigh, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"1354–Bef. Jul 1416":"1354–avant juillet 1416","1354–1416":"1354–1416","1380–1420":"1380–1420","1405–1425":"1405–1425","–Male":"Décédé","1425":"1425","1354":"1354","1420":"1420","1380":"1380","Bef. Jul 1416":"avant juillet 1416","1405":"1405","1416":"1416","Winkley, Devons, England":"Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Winkleigh, Devon, England":"Winkleigh, Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Elizabeth Denebawdo est née en 1354, à Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, fille de Denebawdo. Elle a eu au moins